products.title: Vitra Blackout Sea Green Roller Blind
products.description: Their vitra blackout sea green fabric is a bright, fun green with a hint of blue colour, the stylish shade is modern and contemporary and will work well within the home or office. Blackout fabrics will completely block light from coming through making them a perfect addition for bedrooms and any room that requires maximum light control.
